Name: "Alternating Man-Makers"
Instructions: 10 Man-Makers (YGIY, 35/25 lbs DBs), 20 V-ups (Split Reps).
column8: Reduce Man-Makers to 5 reps per person.

Name: "The Triplet Synchronized"
Instructions: 20 Synchro Wall Balls, 20 Synchro Dumbbell Thrusters (35/25 lbs), 20 Synchro Sit-ups.
column8: Reduce reps to 15 per movement.

Name: "Row/Ski Tax Hold"
Instructions: 2000m Row (Split Reps). While P1 rows, P2 holds a Squat. Switch when P1 finishes set/drops. 2000m Ski (Split Reps), P2 holds a Plank. Switch when P1 finishes set/drops.
column8: Reduce distance to 1500m per machine.

Name: "Barbell Hold Penalty"
Instructions: 15 Power Cleans (135/95 lbs) (YGIY). P2 holds Barbell in Front Rack. Switch when P1 finishes set or P2 drops bar.
column8: Reduce Clean weight to 115/75 lbs.

Name: "Synchro Pulling"
Instructions: Synchronized Pull-ups, Alternating Dumbbell Thrusters (50/35 lbs, YGIY).
column8: Scale Pull-ups to Jumping Pull-ups; reduce DB weight.

Name: "Heavy Sled Partner"
Instructions: 50m Heavy Sled Push (P1 works, P2 rests). 50m Heavy Sled Pull (P2 works, P1 rests). 10 Synchro Burpees.
column8: Reduce sled load; substitute Synchro Burpees for Air Squats.

Name: "Assault Bike Exchange"
Instructions: 300 Cals total (Split Reps). Partners can exchange at any time but must switch every time a partner drops their hands from the handles.
column8: Reduce Cals to 200 total.

Name: "Odd Object Relay"
Instructions: P1 runs 200m carrying a Sandbag (Heavy). P2 completes max reps of Kettlebell Swings (24/16 kg). Switch roles. Score is total swings.
column8: Reduce run to 100m; reduce Sandbag weight.

Name: "The Strict Synchronized"
Instructions: 10 Synchronized Strict Pull-ups, 10 Synchronized Strict Handstand Push-ups.
column8: Scale Strict Pull-ups to Ring Rows; HSPU to Pike Push-ups.

Name: "Barbell Clean Hold"
Instructions: P1 performs 10 Front Squats (135/95 lbs). P2 holds Barbell in the Front Rack. Switch when P1 finishes set or P2 drops bar.
column8: Reduce FS reps to 7; reduce barbell weight.

Name: "Rowing Penalty Chipper"
Instructions: 100 Pull-ups, 100 Box Jumps, 100 Push-ups. Every time a partner breaks or tags out, the other must complete a 250m Row immediately.
column8: Reduce reps to 75; reduce row to 150m.

Name: "EMOM Gymnastic Pacer"
Instructions: Min 1: 10 Toes-to-Bar (Split). Min 2: 10/7 Cal Ski (YGIY). Min 3: 10 Box Jump Overs (Split). Min 4: Rest.
column8: Reduce T2B to Knees-to-Elbow; reduce Ski Cals.

Name: "Team Half Murph"
Instructions: 800m Run (Together). 50 Pull-ups, 100 Push-ups, 150 Air Squats (All Split Reps). 800m Run (Together).
column8: Reduce all bodyweight reps by 25%.

Name: "Alternating C&J"
Instructions: 100 Clean & Jerks (115/75 lbs), performed "I Go, You Go" (P1 does 1, P2 does 1). Every 20 reps, both partners perform 10 Burpees.
column8: Reduce weight to 95/65 lbs.

Name: "Pistol Penalty Hold"
Instructions: P1 performs Max Reps of Ring Rows. P2 holds a Pistol Squat position (bottom, alternating legs every 30s). Switch when P2 breaks hold.
column8: Scale Pistol hold to a 90-degree Front Squat hold.

Name: "Heavy D-Ball Over"
Instructions: 10 D-Ball Over Shoulder (Heavy, YGIY), 10 Synchro Push-ups. 200m Run (Together).
column8: Reduce D-Ball weight; reduce run to 100m.

Name: "Row/Ski Tax Sprint"
Instructions: P1 rows 250m (Max Effort). P2 holds a Chin-Over-Bar. Switch. P1 skis 250m (Max Effort). P2 holds a Plank. Switch.
column8: Reduce distance to 200m.

Name: "The Partner Ladder"
Instructions: Ladder of 2-4-6-8...: Dumbbell Snatch (Alternating, Split Reps), Box Jump Overs (Split Reps).
column8: Use a lighter DB (40/25 lbs).

Name: "Synchro KB Swings"
Instructions: 150 Synchronized Kettlebell Swings (24/16 kg). Every time partners fall out of sync, they must complete 5 Burpees each.
column8: Reduce total reps to 100.

Name: "Weighted Vest Run"
Instructions: 1 Mile Run (Together, one partner wears 20/14lb vest). 50 AbMat Sit-ups (Split Reps). Vest must be exchanged at 800m mark.
column8: Remove the vest; reduce run to 800m.

Name: "Synchro Wall Climbs"
Instructions: 5 Synchronized Wall Walks, 10 Synchro Air Squats.
column8: Scale Wall Walks to Pike Push-ups.

Name: "Clean & Jerk Penalty"
Instructions: 5 Clean & Jerks (185/125 lbs) (YGIY). P2 holds barbell in Back Rack. Switch when P1 finishes set or P2 drops bar.
column8: Reduce C&J weight to 155/105 lbs.

Name: "Ski/Wall Ball Hold"
Instructions: P1 performs Max Cals on Ski Erg. P2 holds a GHD Sit-up position (at 90 degrees). Switch when P2 breaks hold. Score is total Cals.
column8: Substitute GHD hold for a V-up hold.

Name: "Partner Burpee Over"
Instructions: 10 Burpees Over Partner (Partner lies flat on ground, partner works). 10 Air Squats (Synchro).
column8: Reduce rounds to 7.

Name: "Legless Relay"
Instructions: 1 Legless Rope Climb (YGIY), 15 Box Jumps (Split Reps).
column8: Scale to regular Rope Climb or 2:1 Strict Pull-ups.

Name: "Team Triplet Grind"
Instructions: 50 Double Unders (Synchro), 20 Kettlebell Goblet Squats (YGIY), 10 Ring Dips (Split Reps).
column8: Scale DU to Single Unders; scale Ring Dips to Box Dips.

Name: "Alternating Row/Clean"
Instructions: 500m Row (YGIY, P1 does 250m then P2 does 250m). 10 Squat Cleans (135/95 lbs) (YGIY).
column8: Reduce Row to 400m.

Name: "The Sandbag Squat Tax"
Instructions: 10 Sandbag Front Squats (Heavy, YGIY). P2 performs a Wall Sit. Switch when P1 finishes set or P2 drops from wall.
column8: Reduce Sandbag weight.

Name: "Partner Run Penalty"
Instructions: 1600m Run (Together). Every time partners separate by more than 10 ft, both must stop and perform 5 Burpees.
column8: Reduce run to 800m.
